title: Employments in the Netherlands 2020
summary: Overall Labor force in millions has increased over the Year.
Labor force in millions is slightly increasing from 2018 to 2020.
The steepest increase occurs in between the Year 2018 and 2019.
Maximum Labor force in millions, about 8.94 was reported at Year 2020
The lowest Labor force in millions, of value 8.78 was reported at Year 2018
